1.text: The Double Aries influence. Your identity is forged in the fires of self-discovery. You are here to lead, to start, and to be unapologetically yourself.
1.essence: Vitality expressed through immediate action and self-assertion.
1.gift: Unshakable courage and the will to begin.

Aries.10: A warrior king. Your drive for personal recognition is channeled into career and public reputation. You lead with authority.
